UBS Employee Arrested in London Said to Be Kweku Adoboli

-- B y   E l e n a   L o g u t e n k o v a
-- 
2011-09-15T11:08:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/ubs-employee-arrested-in-london-said-to-be-kweku-adoboli.html
The  UBS AG (UBSN)  employee arrested by
 London  police today in connection with the bank’s trading loss
was Kweku Adoboli, said a person familiar with the matter who
requested anonimity.  UBS declined to identify the man who London police said
they arrested earlier today. A person at UBS in London who
picked up Adoboli’s office phone said he wasn’t in today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elena Logutenkova in Zurich at 
 elogutenkova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
